# Daniel Bemba - Cybersecurity Portfolio

![Portfolio Screenshot](./static/images/screenshot.png)

A responsive portfolio website for Daniel Bemba, Cybersecurity Evangelist & Ethical Hacking Expert.

## Features

- **Modern UI Design**: Clean, professional layout with responsive design
- **Dark Mode Toggle**: User-friendly theme switching functionality
- **Comprehensive Sections**:
  - Professional profile with social links
  - About section
  - Skills showcase
  - Projects gallery (21 featured projects)
  - Contact form
- **Optimized Performance**: Fast loading with optimized assets
- **Accessibility**: Semantic HTML5 structure

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (for dark mode toggle and form handling)
- Responsive Design Principles

